      <title>莱西去世后伊朗将于 6 月 28 日举行总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/iran-to-hold-presidential-elections-june-28-after-raisi-s-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据半官方的塔斯尼姆通讯社报道，易卜拉欣·莱西 (Ebrahim Raisi) 周末在直升机失事中丧生后，伊朗将于 6 月 28 日举行总统选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/iran-to-hold-presidential-elections-june-28-after-raisi-s-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:56:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
